snippet.title: ORIOLES VS INDIANS-MLB 9 Innings 18 Gameplay
snippet.description: This is the first gameplay of MLB 9 Innings 18 for 2019 and for the first gameplay it’s the Baltimore Orioles taking on the Cleveland Indians. I’m the home team while the opposing team is the away team, I hope you enjoy this video, if u did be sure you hit the like button, leave your comments and above all else SUBSCRIBE!!
